success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104xyh1665702806859.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/xyh1665702806859.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/xyh1665702806859.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"xyh1665702806859\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      Define Operation\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Define operations for the current component implementation.\n </p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"xyh1665702806859__p_d6524e1_d6525e1_d6526e1\">The <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Details of Operation</span> section of this form shows the specification details for the operation, while the Details of Implementation section enables you to provide implementation-specific information for the operation.</p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"xyh1665702806859__section_y23_rgf_5cc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d449208e61\">Fields</h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"xyh1665702806859__ul_r3z_rgf_5cc\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"xyh1665702806859__li_d3191e1_d3192e1_d3193e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"jrq1665702585385.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/jrq1665702585385.html\" title=\"Name of the development object, which uniquely identifies it.\">Name</a>—For non-Uniface\n               implementations, this name is mapped to the literal name. </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"xyh1665702806859__li_d3194e1_d3195e1_d3196e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"mvb1665702679041.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/mvb1665702679041.html\" title=\"Specify whether the component instance runs synchronously or asynchronously.\">Communication Default</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"xyh1665702806859__li_d3197e1_d3198e1_d3199e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"rki1665702802443.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/rki1665702802443.html\" title=\"List of implementations described by the signature.\">Implementations</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"xyh1665702806859__li_d3200e1_d3201e1_d3202e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"gyk1665702807017.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/gyk1665702807017.html\" title=\"Case-sensitive name for the operation for non-Uniface implementations. The literal name should be a maximum of 64 characters. All NLS characters are valid, but the first character must be a letter.\">Literal Name</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"xyh1665702806859__li_d3203e1_d3204e1_d3205e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"zkx1665702802723.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/zkx1665702802723.html\" title=\"User documentation for the operation's return value.\">Return Value</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"xyh1665702806859__li_d3206e1_d3207e1_d3208e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"cgf1665702807088.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/cgf1665702807088.html\" title=\"Determines whether to use the context pointer specified in the C implementation definition.\">Use Context</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"xyh1665702806859__section_ed3_tgf_5cc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d449208e134\">How to</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"xyh1665702806859__p_d6539e1_d6540e1_d6541e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"uzv1665702678968.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/uzv1665702678968.html\" title=\"Operations are the interfaces to components. Every component has a set of custom-defined operations. You can define these interfaces using the Signature Editor.\">Define Component Operations of a Signature</a>\n</p>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labe